sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant T as Timer
    participant A as TelemetryAggregator
    participant R as TelemetryReader
    participant D as dpstat snapshot
    participant K as Pinned BPF maps
    participant PG as Postgres
    participant SPA as React SPA

    loop every telemetry interval up to 2s
        T->>A: tick
        A->>R: request snapshot
        R->>D: exec subprocess with timeout
        D->>K: read svc_stat and counter and active_config
        K-->>D: per-CPU values
        D-->>R: JSON of active, xdp, node, services
        R-->>A: TelemetrySnapshot or None

        alt reader returned None so gateway offline
            A->>PG: write NodeHealthSnapshot mode offline
        else snapshot present
            Note over A: delta equals current minus previous, reset when negative or version changed
            A->>PG: refresh dp_id to service and tenant cache
            Note over A: first tick seeds baseline and emits no deltas
            A->>PG: upsert TelemetryCounter rows for service and node
            A->>PG: upsert NodeHealthSnapshot with mode version map_error throughput
            A->>PG: prune windows older than retention
        end
        Note over A: on any error log and continue, never crash worker
    end

    SPA->>PG: GET telemetry and health via API every 2s
    PG-->>SPA: latest window with staleness flag
